---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Security Dashboard тАФ Mas Muhammad"
  description="Real-time security analytics dashboard for masmuh.web.id powered by Cloudflare Analytics"
>
  <nav>
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Mas<span>.</span>ID</a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="/">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#skills">Skills</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#experience">Experience</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#projects">Projects</a></li>
      <li><a href="/resume">CV</a></li>
      <li><a href="/security" class="active-link">Security</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <div class="nav-status">
        <span class="status-dot"></span>
        LIVE
      </div>
      <button class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle" title="Toggle theme">
        <span class="theme-icon-dark">тША</span>
        <span class="theme-icon-light">тШ╛</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="security-page">
    <section class="security-hero">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-num">[SECURITY]</span>
        <h1 class="section-title">Dashboard</h1>
        <div class="section-line"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="security-intro">
        <p class="intro-text">
          This dashboard displays <strong>real-time security analytics</strong> from
          <strong>Cloudflare</strong> for <code>masmuh.web.id</code> over the <strong>last 24 hours</strong>.
          Cloudflare automatically filters and blocks threats before they reach the
          server, including DDoS attacks, SQL Injection, cross-site scripting (XSS),
          credential stuffing, and malicious bots.
        </p>
        <div class="intro-details">
          <div class="intro-item">
            <span class="intro-icon">ЁЯЫбя╕П</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Web Application Firewall (WAF)</strong>
              <p>Cloudflare WAF inspects every incoming request and blocks common attack patterns using OWASP rules and real-time signature updates.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="intro-item">
            <span class="intro-icon">ЁЯдЦ</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Bot Management</strong>
              <p>Cloudflare identifies and classifies bot traffic through behavioral analysis, fingerprinting, and machine learning тАФ distinguishing legitimate bots (search engines) from malicious ones (scrapers, attackers).</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="intro-item">
            <span class="intro-icon">ЁЯУК</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Analytics & Monitoring</strong>
              <p>Data is sourced directly from the Cloudflare GraphQL Analytics API, providing accurate, real-time insight into threats blocked at the edge.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="intro-item">
            <span class="intro-icon">ЁЯФН</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Anti-Scraping & Crawl Protection</strong>
              <p>Cloudflare identifies automated scraping tools and aggressive crawlers through behavioral fingerprinting and adaptive rate limiting тАФ blocking unauthorized content extraction while preserving access for legitimate search engines and APIs.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="security-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-icon">ЁЯЫбя╕П</div>
          <div class="stat-value" id="stat-threats">тАФ</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Threats Blocked (24h)</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-icon">ЁЯУК</div>
          <div class="stat-value" id="stat-requests">тАФ</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Total Requests (24h)</div>
        </div>

        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-icon">ЁЯМН</div>
          <div class="stat-value stat-value--country" id="stat-top-country">тАФ</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Top Attacking Country</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-icon">тЪая╕П</div>
          <div class="stat-value" id="stat-rate">тАФ</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Block Rate</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="timeline-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-num">[ANALYTICS]</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Blocked Requests (24h)</h2>
        <div class="section-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="echarts-wrap">
        <div id="timeline-chart" style="height: 320px;"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="countries-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-num">[SOURCE]</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Top Attacking Countries</h2>
        <div class="section-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="echarts-wrap">
        <div id="countries-chart" style="height: 400px;"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="refresh-section">
      <button class="btn-secondary refresh-btn" id="refresh-btn">
        тЖ╗ Refresh Data
      </button>
      <p class="last-updated" id="last-updated">Loading Cloudflare analytics...</p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-left">
      <span>Mas</span>Muhammad ┬й 2026
    </div>
    <div class="footer-center">Senior Backend Engineer</div>
    <div class="footer-right">
      <a href="/"><span>Home</span></a>
      <span>┬╖</span>
      <a href="/resume"><span>CV</span></a>
      <span>┬╖</span>
      <a href="/security"><span>Security</span></a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<script>
import * as echarts from 'echarts';

const formatNumber = n => n.toLocaleString();

const COUNTRY_NAMES = {
  US: 'United States', CN: 'China', RU: 'Russia', BR: 'Brazil', IN: 'India',
  ID: 'Indonesia', GB: 'United Kingdom', DE: 'Germany', FR: 'France', JP: 'Japan',
  KR: 'South Korea', SG: 'Singapore', MY: 'Malaysia', PH: 'Philippines', TH: 'Thailand',
  VN: 'Vietnam', NL: 'Netherlands', AU: 'Australia', CA: 'Canada', IT: 'Italy',
  UA: 'Ukraine', IR: 'Iran', IL: 'Israel', TR: 'Turkey', AR: 'Argentina',
  MX: 'Mexico', NG: 'Nigeria', ZA: 'South Africa', BD: 'Bangladesh', PL: 'Poland',
  SE: 'Sweden', NO: 'Norway', FI: 'Finland', CH: 'Switzerland', AT: 'Austria',
  TW: 'Taiwan', HK: 'Hong Kong', RO: 'Romania', HU: 'Hungary', CZ: 'Czech Republic',
  SK: 'Slovakia', SI: 'Slovenia', HR: 'Croatia', BG: 'Bulgaria', GR: 'Greece',
  PT: 'Portugal', ES: 'Spain', BE: 'Belgium', DK: 'Denmark', IE: 'Ireland',
};

const COUNTRY_FLAGS = {
  US: 'ЁЯЗ║ЁЯЗ╕', CN: 'ЁЯЗиЁЯЗ│', RU: 'ЁЯЗ╖ЁЯЗ║', BR: 'ЁЯЗзЁЯЗ╖', IN: 'ЁЯЗоЁЯЗ│',
  ID: 'ЁЯЗоЁЯЗй', GB: 'ЁЯЗмЁЯЗз', DE: 'ЁЯЗйЁЯЗк', FR: 'ЁЯЗлЁЯЗ╖', JP: 'ЁЯЗпЁЯЗ╡',
  KR: 'ЁЯЗ░ЁЯЗ╖', SG: 'ЁЯЗ╕ЁЯЗм', MY: 'ЁЯЗ▓ЁЯЗ╛', PH: 'ЁЯЗ╡ЁЯЗн', TH: 'ЁЯЗ╣ЁЯЗн',
  VN: 'ЁЯЗ╗ЁЯЗ│', NL: 'ЁЯЗ│ЁЯЗ▒', AU: 'ЁЯЗжЁЯЗ║', CA: 'ЁЯЗиЁЯЗж', IT: 'ЁЯЗоЁЯЗ╣',
  UA: 'ЁЯЗ║ЁЯЗж', IR: 'ЁЯЗоЁЯЗ╖', IL: 'ЁЯЗоЁЯЗ▒', TR: 'ЁЯЗ╣ЁЯЗ╖', AR: 'ЁЯЗжЁЯЗ╖',
  MX: 'ЁЯЗ▓ЁЯЗ╜', NG: 'ЁЯЗ│ЁЯЗм', ZA: 'ЁЯЗ┐ЁЯЗж', BD: 'ЁЯЗзЁЯЗй', PL: 'ЁЯЗ╡ЁЯЗ▒',
  SE: 'ЁЯЗ╕ЁЯЗк', NO: 'ЁЯЗ│ЁЯЗ┤', FI: 'ЁЯЗлЁЯЗо', CH: 'ЁЯЗиЁЯЗн', AT: 'ЁЯЗжЁЯЗ╣',
  TW: 'ЁЯЗ╣ЁЯЗ╝', HK: 'ЁЯЗнЁЯЗ░', RO: 'ЁЯЗ╖ЁЯЗ┤', HU: 'ЁЯЗнЁЯЗ║', CZ: 'ЁЯЗиЁЯЗ┐',
  SK: 'ЁЯЗ╕ЁЯЗ░', SI: 'ЁЯЗ╕ЁЯЗо', HR: 'ЁЯЗнЁЯЗ╖', BG: 'ЁЯЗзЁЯЗм', GR: 'ЁЯЗмЁЯЗ╖',
  PT: 'ЁЯЗ╡ЁЯЗ╣', ES: 'ЁЯЗкЁЯЗ╕', BE: 'ЁЯЗзЁЯЗк', DK: 'ЁЯЗйЁЯЗ░', IE: 'ЁЯЗоЁЯЗк',
};

function countryName(code) {
  return COUNTRY_NAMES[code] || code || 'Unknown';
}

function flagFor(code) {
  if (!code || code === 'Unknown') return 'ЁЯМН';
  if (COUNTRY_FLAGS[code]) return COUNTRY_FLAGS[code];
  const l = code.toUpperCase().split('');
  if (l.length === 2) return String.fromCodePoint(0x1F1E6 + l[0].charCodeAt(0) - 65) + String.fromCodePoint(0x1F1E6 + l[1].charCodeAt(0) - 65);
  return 'ЁЯМН';
}

const EC = {
  bg: '#0c1526',
  text: '#a0b3cc',
  textLight: '#e0e6f1',
  cyan: '#00c8ff',
  green: '#00ff9d',
  orange: '#ff6b35',
  purple: '#a78bfa',
  slate: '#64748b',
  border: '#1a2a40',
};

let timelineChart, countriesChart;

function initCharts() {
  if (timelineChart) timelineChart.dispose();
  if (countriesChart) countriesChart.dispose();
  timelineChart = echarts.init(document.getElementById('timeline-chart'), null, { renderer: 'svg' });
  countriesChart = echarts.init(document.getElementById('countries-chart'), null, { renderer: 'svg' });
}

function renderTimeline(timeline) {
  if (!timelineChart || !timeline) return;
  const hours = timeline.map(t => t.hour);
  const counts = timeline.map(t => t.count);
  timelineChart.setOption({
    backgroundColor: 'transparent',
    tooltip: {
      trigger: 'axis',
      backgroundColor: EC.bg,
      borderColor: EC.border,
      textStyle: { color: EC.textLight, fontFamily: 'var(--font-mono)', fontSize: 12 },
      formatter: p => `${p[0].name}<br/><span style="color:${EC.cyan}">тЧП</span> Blocked: ${formatNumber(p[0].value)}`,
    },
    grid: { left: 50, right: 20, top: 20, bottom: 30 },
    xAxis: {
      type: 'category',
      data: hours,
      axisLine: { lineStyle: { color: EC.border } },
      axisTick: { show: false },
      axisLabel: { color: EC.text, fontFamily: 'var(--font-mono)', fontSize: 10, interval: 2 },
    },
    yAxis: {
      type: 'value',
      splitLine: { lineStyle: { color: EC.border, type: 'dashed', opacity: 0.4 } },
      axisLine: { show: false },
      axisTick: { show: false },
      axisLabel: { color: EC.text, fontFamily: 'var(--font-mono)', fontSize: 10 },
    },
    series: [{
      type: 'bar',
      data: counts,
      itemStyle: {
        color: new echarts.graphic.LinearGradient(0, 0, 0, 1, [
          { offset: 0, color: EC.cyan },
          { offset: 1, color: 'rgba(0,200,255,0.1)' },
        ]),
        borderRadius: [3, 3, 0, 0],
      },
      barWidth: '60%',
      animationDuration: 800,
    }],
  });
}

function renderCountries(topCountries) {
  if (!countriesChart || !topCountries) return;
  const total = topCountries.reduce((s, c) => s + c.count, 0);
  const colors = [EC.cyan, EC.green, EC.orange, EC.purple, EC.slate];
  const data = topCountries.slice(0, 5).map((c, i) => ({
    name: flagFor(c.country) + ' ' + countryName(c.country),
    value: c.count,
    pct: ((c.count / total) * 100).toFixed(1) + '%',
    itemStyle: { color: colors[i] },
  }));

  countriesChart.setOption({
    backgroundColor: 'transparent',
    tooltip: {
      backgroundColor: EC.bg,
      borderColor: EC.border,
      textStyle: { color: EC.textLight, fontFamily: 'var(--font-mono)', fontSize: 12 },
      formatter: p => `${p.name}<br/><span style="color:${p.color}">тЧП</span> ${formatNumber(p.value)} (${p.data.pct})`,
    },
    legend: {
      orient: 'vertical',
      right: 10,
      top: 'center',
      textStyle: { color: EC.text, fontFamily: 'var(--font-body)', fontSize: 12 },
      itemWidth: 10,
      itemHeight: 10,
      itemGap: 14,
      icon: 'circle',
      formatter: name => {
        const item = data.find(d => d.name === name);
        return `{name|${name}}  {pct|${item ? item.pct : ''}}`;
      },
      textStyle: {
        rich: {
          name: { color: EC.textLight, fontFamily: 'var(--font-body)', fontSize: 12, width: 180 },
          pct: { color: EC.cyan, fontFamily: 'var(--font-mono)', fontSize: 11, align: 'right' },
        },
      },
    },
    series: [{
      type: 'pie',
      radius: ['45%', '70%'],
      center: ['35%', '50%'],
      avoidLabelOverlap: true,
      itemStyle: { borderRadius: 6, borderColor: EC.bg, borderWidth: 3 },
      label: { show: false },
      emphasis: {
        label: {
          show: true,
          fontSize: 14,
          fontWeight: 'bold',
          color: EC.textLight,
          formatter: p => formatNumber(p.value),
        },
        itemStyle: { shadowBlur: 10, shadowColor: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.3)' },
      },
      data,
      animationType: 'scale',
      animationEasing: 'elasticOut',
      animationDuration: 1000,
    }],
  });
}

function populateUI(data) {
  document.getElementById('stat-threats').textContent = formatNumber(data.threatsBlocked);
  document.getElementById('stat-requests').textContent = formatNumber(data.requestsToday);

  const rate = data.requestsToday > 0
    ? ((data.threatsBlocked / data.requestsToday) * 100).toFixed(1) + '%'
    : '0%';
  document.getElementById('stat-rate').textContent = rate;

  const top = data.topCountries?.[0];
  const topEl = document.getElementById('stat-top-country');
  if (top && top.country) {
    topEl.textContent = flagFor(top.country) + ' ' + countryName(top.country);
  }

  renderTimeline(data.timeline);
  renderCountries(data.topCountries);
}

async function loadData() {
  const refreshBtn = document.getElementById('refresh-btn');
  const lastUpdated = document.getElementById('last-updated');
  if (refreshBtn) refreshBtn.disabled = true;
  if (lastUpdated) lastUpdated.textContent = 'Connecting to Cloudflare...';

  try {
    const res = await fetch('/.netlify/functions/security');
    if (!res.ok) throw new Error('API error');
    const data = await res.json();
    populateUI(data);
    if (lastUpdated) lastUpdated.textContent = 'Last updated: ' + new Date().toLocaleTimeString();
  } catch {
    const SAMPLE = {
      threatsBlocked: 12847,
      requestsToday: 4291,
      timeline: [
        { hour: '00:00', count: 42 }, { hour: '01:00', count: 38 },
        { hour: '02:00', count: 25 }, { hour: '03:00', count: 18 },
        { hour: '04:00', count: 22 }, { hour: '05:00', count: 31 },
        { hour: '06:00', count: 45 }, { hour: '07:00', count: 67 },
        { hour: '08:00', count: 89 }, { hour: '09:00', count: 120 },
        { hour: '10:00', count: 145 }, { hour: '11:00', count: 132 },
        { hour: '12:00', count: 98 }, { hour: '13:00', count: 87 },
        { hour: '14:00', count: 112 }, { hour: '15:00', count: 95 },
        { hour: '16:00', count: 78 }, { hour: '17:00', count: 65 },
        { hour: '18:00', count: 54 }, { hour: '19:00', count: 48 },
        { hour: '20:00', count: 52 }, { hour: '21:00', count: 43 },
        { hour: '22:00', count: 38 }, { hour: '23:00', count: 29 },
      ],
      topCountries: [
        { country: 'ID', count: 4291 }, { country: 'CN', count: 2156 },
        { country: 'RU', count: 1843 }, { country: 'US', count: 1247 },
        { country: 'BR', count: 956 },
      ],
    };
    populateUI(SAMPLE);
    if (lastUpdated) lastUpdated.textContent = 'Sample data тАФ connect to Netlify for live updates.';
  } finally {
    if (refreshBtn) refreshBtn.disabled = false;
  }
}

initCharts();
window.addEventListener('resize', () => {
  timelineChart?.resize();
  countriesChart?.resize();
});

document.getElementById('refresh-btn')?.addEventListener('click', loadData);
loadData();
</script>

<style>
  .security-page {
    padding-top: 100px;
  }

  .security-hero {
    padding: 60px;
  }

  .security-intro {
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 32px;
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .intro-text strong {
    color: var(--cyan);
  }

  .intro-text code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--green);
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .intro-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .intro-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 16px;
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .intro-icon {
    font-size: 24px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .intro-item div {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .intro-item strong {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--cyan);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .intro-item p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .security-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 28px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .stat-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 3px;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--cyan);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-bright);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .stat-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: -2px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .stat-value--country {
    font-size: 32px;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .timeline-section,
  .countries-section {
    padding: 60px;
  }

  .echarts-wrap {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .refresh-section {
    padding: 60px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .refresh-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .security-hero,
    .timeline-section,
    .countries-section,
    .refresh-section {
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }

    .stat-value {
      font-size: 32px;
    }

    .stat-value--country {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .intro-details {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
